            },
            "loading": "lazy",
            "decoding": "async"
          }}></img>{`
  `}</a>{`
    `}</span></p>
    <p>{`The next two steps are "Post-Build". This time, two different types. The first one is "Publish JUnit test result report". It has a single parameter which is the XML file. Mine is set to "coverage/junit.xml". The second task is a "Publish Cobertura Coverage Report". It also takes a single parameter which is the coverage.xml file. Mine is set to "coverage/coverage.xml".`}</p>
    <p><span parentName="p" {...{
